<header>

<h1 class="main-title">Đóa hoa nào cho mẹ?</h1>
<div class="meta clearfix">
<time><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i>02:45 PM - 08/03/2017 <span class="symbol">Thanh Niên Online</span></time>
</div>
